Why?<br>
<br>
I am levelling as fast as I can (4 1/2 days play time, no PL) to fight in RvR. In a group strealth is useless as it is too slow to setup and you may end up pulling aggro off the tank and then die on high purps.<br>
<br>
I now have 29 Axe, 28 Crit Strike and 7 stealth (before item bonuses). I deliver serious damage in a group and advertise myself as a &quot;29 SB, no stealth and a big axe&quot;.<br>
<br>
I will continue to not buy stealth, not for the benefit of free stealth, but for the extra damage and chance to hit in combat. This will change at about 36, when I will bump up stealth for RvR. (I will stop buying axe earlier and save the points so I can buy a large whack of stealth in one go).<br>
<br>
My end game template is:  xx no bonus (xx)  bonus inc<br>
<br>
Axe 39 (50)<br>
Crit Strike 39 (50) <br>
Stealth 40 (50)<br>
LA/Env 36 (47) - I may bump up CS some more if the 50 cap is not introduced. (Currently you do more dam with a skill of 52 than 50, even though there is meant to be a cap at 50 - I believe)<br>
<br>
Hope this helps,<br>
